  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Bowser overturned with petrol",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mirigama police said that a bowser carrying petrol met with an accident at Halukama hill on Thangowitha road in Mirigama today (23) afternoon.",
        "The police said that 33,600 liters of petrol, which was transported from Muthurajawela to Peradana, was in the bowser.",
        "Preliminary investigations have revealed that the accident occurred due to a sudden backward movement of the bowser from the Halukama hill climb."
      ],
